              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Charged particles were detected",
                "using telescope consisting of two double-sided",
                "silicon strip detectors (DSSSD) was placed at forward",
                "angle. E detectcor was 128 x 128 DSSSD with active",
                "area of 97.2 x 97.2 mm2 and thickness of 500 mu-m. dE",
                "detector was 16 x 16 DSSSD with active area of 49.5 x",
                "49.5 mm2 and thickness of 38 mu-m. E and dE detectors",
                "were placed 100 mm and 50 mm away from target,",
                "respectivelly and covered laboratory theta angles",
                "between 15 deg and 89 deg."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Another identical DSSSD E detector was placed",
                "at a distance 100 mm from the target at backward",
                "angle, covering theta laboratoty angles between 87",
                "deg and 161 deg."
              ]
            }
          ],
